Create following unit test and then create enough production code to pass them and
then finally refactor your code.

***********************************************************************************
1. Can create instance of checkout class
2. Can add item price
3. Can add an item
4. Can calculate the current total
5. Can add multiple items and get correct total
6. Can add a discount rule
7. Can apply discount rule to the total
8. Exception is thrown for an item added without a price





